Changes:
  * Azure transfer class improvements

  * Fix #1398. Try a close when EOFError is encountered. (FTP)

  * nodupe improvements (#1382): add path_only and name bases. IMPORTANT:

  * Fix #884: add option to configure "safe" characters that should not get

  * Fix #1395: directory removal race condition (impacted HPC mirroring)

  * Fix #1393: NameError: name 'chunksize_from_str' is not defined

  * S3 transfer class improvements (allows anonymous access, creates buckets

  * Fix #1299: bulletin renamer fix

  * Fix #1373: cp is in /bin (default accelCpCommand was wrong)

  * New #1371: Sets the product name and version for AMQP connections

  * New #1369: add attachment support to email sender plugin


